{
  "texts": [
    "An initial screening of the search results was conducted based on the title and abstract of each study.",
    "Studies that appeared irrelevant or did not meet the inclusion criteria were excluded at this stage.",
    "The preliminary screening procedure assisted in reducing the total number of studies to a more manageable number for detailed evaluation.",
    "The remaining studies underwent an examination of the complete text to evaluate their relevance and the level of methodological rigor, and contribution to the field.",
    "During this stage, the criteria for both inclusion and exclusion were applied in detail, evaluating each study's objectives, methodology, findings, and overall quality."
  ]
}